{"text_id":118289,"tokens":["##"," How"," to"," Mour","n","\n\n","**","Know"," that"," everyone"," has"," their"," own"," unique"," experience"," with"," grief",".**"," It"," is"," not"," a"," linear"," process"," and"," can"," feel"," like"," a"," chaotic"," whirlwind"," of"," emotions","."," Loss"," can"," come"," in"," many"," forms",","," from"," the"," death"," of"," a"," loved"," one"," to"," the"," end"," of"," a"," relationship",","," the"," loss"," of"," a"," job",","," or"," the"," death"," of"," a"," dream",".","\n\n","**","Acknowledge"," that"," there"," are"," many"," kinds"," of"," loss",".**"," Each"," loss"," is"," unique"," and"," will"," be"," processed"," differently","."," There"," is"," no"," right"," or"," wrong"," way"," to"," grieve",".","\n\n","**","Recognize"," that"," \u2018","stages","\u2019"," of"," mourning"," do"," not"," really"," exist",".**"," The"," idea"," of"," stages"," (","denial",","," anger",","," bargaining",","," depression",","," acceptance",")"," was"," intended"," as"," a"," guide",","," not"," a"," rigid"," formula","."," Your"," experience"," will"," likely"," be"," fluid"," and"," not"," fit"," into"," these"," arbitrary"," categories",".","\n\n","**","Dist","inguish"," between"," grief"," and"," mourning",".**"," Grief"," is"," the"," emotional"," response"," to"," loss",","," while"," mourning"," is"," the"," process"," of"," integrating"," that"," loss"," into"," your"," life","."," ","\n\n","**","Learn"," about"," the"," necessary"," \u201c","tasks","\u201d"," of"," mourning",".**"," These"," include"," acknowledging"," your"," loss",","," expressing"," your"," emotions",","," caring"," for"," yourself"," physically"," and"," emotionally",","," and"," eventually"," returning"," to"," life",".","\n\n","**","Acknowledge"," that"," you"," and"," others"," may"," not"," experience"," grief"," the"," same"," way",".**"," Your"," personality",","," prior"," experiences",","," and"," cultural"," background"," will"," all"," influence"," your"," grieving"," process",".","\n\n","**","Recognize"," physical"," symptoms"," of"," grief",":**"," Fatigue",","," pain"," in"," the"," body",","," difficulty"," sleeping",","," headaches",","," and"," changes"," in"," appetite",".","\n\n","**","Recognize"," emotional"," symptoms"," of"," grief",":**"," Feeling"," overwhelmed",","," numb",","," sad",","," angry",","," guilty",","," and"," anxious",".","\n\n","**","Recognize"," signs"," of"," grief"," in"," children",":**"," Increased"," aggression",","," withdrawal"," from"," others",","," decreased"," interest"," in"," activities",","," difficulty"," concentrating",","," and"," regression"," in"," social"," or"," academic"," development",".","\n\n","**","Recognize"," signs"," of"," complicated"," grief",":**"," Persistent"," grief"," that"," lasts"," for"," more"," than"," a"," year",","," intrusive"," thoughts"," about"," the"," deceased",","," a"," desire"," to"," harm"," oneself"," or"," others",","," and"," feeling"," emotionally"," numb",".","\n\n","**","Acknowledge"," your"," emotions",".**"," Let"," yourself"," feel"," the"," full"," range"," of"," emotions"," associated"," with"," your"," loss",".","\n\n","**","Express"," your"," feelings"," through"," a"," tangible"," medium",":**"," Writing",","," painting",","," music",","," or"," other"," creative"," outlets"," can"," be"," helpful"," in"," processing"," grief",".","\n\n","**","Acknowledge"," that"," your"," grief"," is"," yours",".**"," It"," is"," unique"," and"," personal","."," Do"," not"," feel"," pressured"," to"," share"," or"," compare"," your"," experience"," with"," others",".","\n\n","**","Maintain"," your"," physical"," health",".**"," Eat"," nourishing"," foods",","," get"," enough"," sleep",","," and"," exercise"," regularly"," to"," support"," your"," emotional"," well","-","being",".","\n\n","**","Avoid"," using"," alcohol",","," drugs",","," or"," food"," to"," deal"," with"," your"," grief",".**"," These"," substances"," can"," temporarily"," numb"," the"," pain"," but"," will"," ultimately"," worsen"," your"," grief"," in"," the"," long"," run",".","\n\n","**","Do"," things"," that"," you"," enjoy",".**"," Engaging"," in"," activities"," that"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}